high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink.
Grab the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the edge of the table.
Slice the potato that is farthest away.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Head back to the table where the sliced potato is.
Grab a potato slice.
Turn around back to the fridge.
Chill the sliced potato for 3 seconds.
Turn around and walk then face right to the toaster.
Place the potato slice in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato slice in front of the toaster.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the front of the sink
Pick up the knife in the sink
Turn around, go to the table
Cut the potato on the table
Turn right, go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn right, go to the table
Pick up a potato slice from the table
Turn right, go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the potato slice from the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn right after the sink
Put the potato slice on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cool a slice

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the left side of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the left side of the silver counter.
Slice the potato to the right of the tomato on the table.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge on the second shelf and close the door.
Turn right and return to the silver counter on the right.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on the right.
Put the slice of potato inside the fridge on the second shelf to the left of the knife, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the counter with the toaster on the right.
Put the chilled slice of potato in front of the toaster on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill a knife and place a chilled slice of potato on a counter.
